flowchart LR
  B[Browser] --> L[LoginServlet]
  L --> S[AuthenticationService]
  S --> D[UserDao]
  D --> O[(Oracle USERS / ROLES)]
  O --> D --> S
  S --> P{BCrypt verifies?}
  P -->|Yes| X[Reset attempts and create safe session]
  X --> DB[Dashboard]
  P -->|No| F[Increment failed attempts]
  F --> Q{Five failures?}
  Q -->|Yes| K[Lock account]
  Q -->|No| L
